# Brand Brief proposal artifacts.
# Everything under proposals/ is regenerable: timestamped dirs are written by
# ds-author MCP on every run, and curated <slug>/ dirs (brief/plan/tasks) are
# AI-authored throwaway specs. Only the README is tracked as documentation.
packages/brand-brief/proposals/*
!packages/brand-brief/proposals/README.md

